Package: fortune-zh
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, fortune-mod
Description: Chinese Data files for fortune
 This package contains the Chinese data files for fortune in
 UTF-8 encoding.
 .
 Those data files are included:
  * tang300 (300 Tang Poems)
  * song100 (100 Song Poems)
  * chinese (Misc chinese cookie)
 .
 They are classical Chinese poems or Chinese literature, 
 all of them are parts of Chinese Culture.
